longBusinessSummary: EV Charging USA, Inc. focuses on providing electric vehicle (EV) charging services and charging stations. Its charging services and stations enable EV drivers to recharge their vehicles at commercial locations or in their own garages. The company was founded in 2013 and is headquartered in Chicago, Illinois.
